34:26.793 --> 34:30.096
I... I get it... family.

34:30.130 --> 34:32.630
You got to go back. But...

34:40.473 --> 34:42.775
Remember this?

34:42.811 --> 34:44.447
The rolex thing. What...

34:44.482 --> 34:46.447
Whatever happened to the guy
who used to sell us those?

34:46.483 --> 34:49.114
Jin Kang? He got deported.

34:49.149 --> 34:53.484
This is the last one. I say we go for it.

34:53.518 --> 34:55.152
No. Oh, come on.

34:55.187 --> 34:56.621
Last time, we did what? $600?

34:56.655 --> 34:59.356
The hot streak we're on,
I bet we break a grand, easy.

34:59.390 --> 35:01.590
I could lend you some cash.

35:01.624 --> 35:03.425
I don't need the money, Jimmy.

35:03.459 --> 35:04.992
I need this.

35:05.027 --> 35:06.127
Come on.

35:06.161 --> 35:07.962
You say you're happy
doing wills or whatever,

35:07.997 --> 35:09.929
good for you, man, seriously.

35:09.964 --> 35:10.996
But I got to tell you...

35:11.030 --> 35:14.833
Standpipes ain't cutting it for me, man.

35:14.867 --> 35:17.802
I got nothing, Jimmy.

35:17.837 --> 35:20.068
Give me this.

35:21.903 --> 35:23.203
Give me this, man.

35:23.238 --> 35:24.538
I can't do it.

35:24.572 --> 35:26.172
Come on. Give me this.

35:26.207 --> 35:27.306
Marco. Give me this.

35:27.340 --> 35:29.141
Come on. Come on. Buddy, listen to me.

35:29.175 --> 35:30.309
I'm listening. Come on.

35:30.343 --> 35:31.644
Hey. Just one last time.

35:31.679 --> 35:32.980
Come on. I'm not being hypnotized.

35:33.014 --> 35:34.815
No? Okay. Come on, one more time.

35:34.850 --> 35:35.950
I can't do it.

35:35.985 --> 35:37.386
Just one more... one more.

35:37.420 --> 35:38.889
Hey, listen to me. Just listen to you.

35:38.924 --> 35:40.425
- Yeah, I'm listening. Come on.
- No.

36:46.332 --> 36:49.970
Yeah!

36:50.004 --> 36:51.304
It's got to come from the gut, man.

36:51.339 --> 36:52.473
Yeah. Yeah.

36:54.679 --> 36:57.146
Oh, that's crazy.

36:57.180 --> 36:58.980
Just like a wolf. Go ahead.

36:59.015 --> 37:00.815
No, deeper, deeper.

37:01.951 --> 37:04.920
Yeah, and you do that
right at the moment of,

37:04.954 --> 37:06.254
you know, pure joy...

37:06.288 --> 37:08.255
Yeah... And it will escalate it 10...

37:08.289 --> 37:10.761
10 times.

37:10.795 --> 37:12.596
- There's something...
- Hey.

37:12.631 --> 37:14.797
- It's prehistoric.
- Hey, hey. Look.

37:24.448 --> 37:27.751
$50, $200, $400.

37:27.786 --> 37:29.589
Whose is it? I don't know.

37:30.659 --> 37:32.294
There's got to be 1,000 bucks in here.

37:32.328 --> 37:35.296
Somebody must have...

37:35.330 --> 37:37.965
Oh.

37:37.999 --> 37:40.169
Oh, damn.

37:50.118 --> 37:51.919
Is he, uh...

37:51.954 --> 37:53.288
I don't know.

38:25.916 --> 38:29.718
Hey, buddy, you with us?

38:29.752 --> 38:33.556
Look, the guy's just had too many.

38:33.591 --> 38:37.559
I say we move on. You want to split this?

38:37.593 --> 38:40.230
Marco, you okay?

38:40.265 --> 38:42.231
Marco?

38:42.265 --> 38:43.731
What... do you know this guy?

38:43.765 --> 38:46.235
Hey, call 911.

38:46.269 --> 38:48.608
Call 911!

38:51.244 --> 38:52.579
Hey!

38:58.754 --> 39:00.054
I need an ambulance.

39:00.088 --> 39:01.723
My friend's having a heart attack.

39:01.757 --> 39:03.728
We're in an alley,

39:03.762 --> 39:05.629
uh, southeast of Lasalle and Shermer.

39:05.663 --> 39:07.464
No, I-i don't know.

39:07.498 --> 39:08.798
He was like this when I found him.

39:08.832 --> 39:10.265
Hey, hold...

39:10.300 --> 39:12.032
Marco, Marco, you with me?

39:12.066 --> 39:14.534
You with me? I screwed up.

39:14.569 --> 39:16.903
No, you did... you did good, buddy.

39:16.937 --> 39:18.404
Just hold on, all right?
They're on their way.

39:18.438 --> 39:19.738
They'll be here in a minute.

39:19.772 --> 39:20.738
Jimmy, you know what?

39:20.773 --> 39:22.073
Just s-save your breath, okay?

39:22.107 --> 39:23.540
You're gonna be fine.

39:23.575 --> 39:27.278
This was the greatest week of my life.

39:32.951 --> 39:35.253
Hey.

39:35.287 --> 39:36.755
Hey, hey, hey.

39:36.789 --> 39:37.989
Hang in there! Hey!

39:38.023 --> 39:41.323
Hey! Hey!

39:41.358 --> 39:42.659
Hey, wake up, man!

39:42.693 --> 39:45.762
Come on! Marco, buddy!

39:48.365 --> 39:49.665
Help!

39:51.701 --> 39:53.569
Anybody!

39:56.801 --> 39:58.002
Marco!

40:09.400 --> 40:12.034
- Hey, Jimmy.
- Oh, hey, bud.

40:12.100 --> 40:13.935
Can I bum one?

40:24.252 --> 40:26.219
Is that his?

40:26.253 --> 40:30.225
Yeah. His mom gave it to me.

40:30.260 --> 40:31.726
Thought it looked familiar.

40:31.761 --> 40:33.225
I figured I'd wear it today,

40:33.260 --> 40:35.059
but I don't know.

40:35.092 --> 40:37.059
I'm not a big ring guy, so...

40:38.527 --> 40:42.196
Still. Could be worth a couple of bucks.

40:56.210 --> 40:58.511
Better head back.

40:58.546 --> 41:00.382
See you inside.

41:23.514 --> 41:24.481
Hey.

41:24.515 --> 41:26.652
Is this Ferris Bueller?

41:26.686 --> 41:28.488
Speaking.

41:28.523 --> 41:30.121
I don't want to interrupt your big day off.

41:30.156 --> 41:32.123
Just checking in. What are you up to?

41:32.157 --> 41:35.127
You know, burning down the place.

41:35.162 --> 41:36.764
I wouldn't expect any less.

41:36.798 --> 41:42.272
So, whatever it was, did you
get it out of your system?

41:42.306 --> 41:44.275
Yep, all gone.

41:44.310 --> 41:47.111
Good. I want to run something by you.

41:47.145 --> 41:50.446
The sandpiper case...
It's getting too big for hhm.

41:50.480 --> 41:52.647
Howard's decided to partner
with another firm.

41:52.682 --> 41:54.816
Davis and Main. You heard of them?

41:54.850 --> 41:56.985
- Sure, up in Santa Fe.
- Right.

41:57.020 --> 42:01.421
Well, they've heard of you, too,
and they're interested.

42:01.455 --> 42:03.587
They want to make you an offer
contingent on an interview.

42:03.621 --> 42:05.253
They've got a partner-track
position in mind.

42:05.287 --> 42:06.420
Wait. What?

42:06.454 --> 42:08.924
Partner track? What are you talking about?

42:08.958 --> 42:10.590
I'm talking about
there's an office in Santa Fe

42:10.625 --> 42:13.592
with your name on it, or there could be,

42:13.626 --> 42:16.030
and you'd be working on your case.

42:16.064 --> 42:19.634
I... well, I...

42:19.669 --> 42:23.170
I don't even, uh...

42:23.204 --> 42:25.705
Chuck wouldn't like it.

42:25.740 --> 42:27.373
Chuck has no say in this.

42:27.407 --> 42:28.874
You wouldn't be working for HHM,

42:28.908 --> 42:31.543
and Chuck can't tell
Davis and Main who to hire.

42:31.577 --> 42:32.677
Why me?

42:32.712 --> 42:34.847
Is this like a tax write-off
or a charity thing?

42:34.881 --> 42:36.280
What's the angle, huh?

42:36.315 --> 42:38.950
Jimmy, we've been talking to your clients,

42:38.984 --> 42:40.152
the sandpiper residents,

42:40.186 --> 42:42.489
and they ask about you
every chance they get.

42:42.523 --> 42:44.992
I don't know what it is,
but you have a way with them.

42:45.026 --> 42:48.196
Hey. Old people love me.

42:48.230 --> 42:52.368
So... Sounds good?

42:55.571 --> 42:58.874
Kim, I can't imagine what
you did to make this happen.

42:58.908 --> 43:01.476
Thank you.

43:01.510 --> 43:02.810
I didn't do anything... much.

43:02.845 --> 43:06.481
And believe it or not,
Howard's been pushing this, too.

43:06.515 --> 43:08.083
Good, old Howard.

43:08.118 --> 43:10.254
Listen, we're gonna be down
in judge Murray's court

43:10.289 --> 43:11.922
on Thursday at 11:00.

43:11.956 --> 43:13.923
The Davis and Main people will be there.

43:13.957 --> 43:16.091
It'd be the perfect chance
for you to meet them.

43:16.125 --> 43:18.259
Thursday at 11:00.
All right, I'll be there.

43:18.294 --> 43:19.762
Thanks, Kim, really.

43:19.796 --> 43:21.598
I'll see you then.

43:32.946 --> 43:35.917
All the originals
need to be copied and filed.

43:35.951 --> 43:38.589
See, I've written right here
on the box... "Copy and file."

43:38.624 --> 43:40.259
That's to make it as clear as possible.

43:40.294 --> 43:42.594
Got it, Mr. Mcgill. Anything else?

43:42.629 --> 43:43.928
Well, on the grocery front,

43:43.963 --> 43:45.764
almost everything was right this time.

43:45.798 --> 43:47.600
- Great.
- Almost.

43:47.635 --> 43:50.071
Um, it's a small thing, but to my taste,

43:50.106 --> 43:52.241
the, uh, Granny Smith apples
are a bit too tart.

43:52.275 --> 43:54.244
- Those are the green ones, right?
- Right.

43:54.279 --> 43:57.080
I prefer the red ones,
but not red delicious.

43:57.114 --> 43:58.948
Those are generally tasteless.

43:58.982 --> 44:00.582
Fujis should be in season.

44:00.616 --> 44:03.053
It's not a major issue, but...

44:03.088 --> 44:04.723
- Yeah.
- Fuji apples.

44:04.757 --> 44:05.723
Okay.

44:05.758 --> 44:07.722
Oh, and I'd like to try soy milk,

44:07.756 --> 44:08.956
so maybe a half gallon of that.

44:08.991 --> 44:11.127
You got it.

44:11.161 --> 44:12.628
Well, thank you, Ernesto.

44:12.663 --> 44:16.296
I appreciate your attention to detail.

44:16.330 --> 44:19.999
Do you need to write any of this down?

44:20.033 --> 44:21.833
'Cause it's okay if you do.

44:21.867 --> 44:23.668
You know, just to be sure.

44:25.371 --> 44:27.839
So, Fuji apples.

44:45.900 --> 44:47.199
Hey, Ernie.

44:47.233 --> 44:49.034
Hey. How you doing, man?

44:49.069 --> 44:50.203
Good, good.

44:50.237 --> 44:52.869
So, Howard's got you
looking after Chuck, huh?

44:52.904 --> 44:54.804
Yeah. It's a few extra bucks, you know?

44:54.839 --> 44:56.174
How's he doing?

44:56.209 --> 44:58.343
Seems okay, like usual.

44:58.377 --> 45:00.176
I'd say we could grab a beer,

45:00.210 --> 45:02.345
but they're waiting on all that
paperwork back at the office...

45:02.380 --> 45:03.681
You know how it is.

45:03.715 --> 45:05.350
Don't I, though?

45:05.384 --> 45:07.017
See you, Jimmy.

45:07.052 --> 45:08.884
Uh, see you 'round, ernie.

45:47.553 --> 45:52.024
You done business with him before?

45:52.059 --> 45:53.693
Right.

45:53.728 --> 45:56.361
Yeah. I'll be there.

46:24.622 --> 46:27.090
Davis and Main and Mcgill.

46:29.258 --> 46:30.892
Great to meet you.

46:30.926 --> 46:33.557
Nice to meet you, gentlemen.

46:33.591 --> 46:35.892
It's good to meet you.

46:35.927 --> 46:38.094
Nice...

47:03.951 --> 47:05.651
Well, that was quick.

47:05.686 --> 47:08.320
- No charge.
- Help me out here.

47:08.354 --> 47:14.326
Did I dream it, or did I have
$1,600,000 on my desk in cash?

47:14.761 --> 47:17.564
When I close my eyes, I can still see it.

47:17.598 --> 47:20.798
It's burned into my retinas
like I was staring into the sun.

47:20.832 --> 47:23.467
No one on God's green earth knew we had it.

47:23.502 --> 47:25.137
We could have split it 50/50.

47:25.171 --> 47:31.140
We could have gone home
with $800,000 each, tax-free.

47:31.674 --> 47:33.644
Your point being?

47:33.678 --> 47:36.279
Why didn't we? What stopped us?

47:36.314 --> 47:40.247
I remember you saying something
about doing the right thing.

47:40.281 --> 47:42.751
I don't even know what that means.

47:44.021 --> 47:45.988
You want to know
why I didn't take that money?

47:46.022 --> 47:47.990
Is that what you're asking?

47:48.024 --> 47:50.126
Yeah, that's what I'm asking.

47:50.160 --> 47:53.462
Me, personally... I was hired to do a job.

47:53.497 --> 47:56.533
I did it. That's as far as it goes.

47:56.567 --> 48:00.538
Yeah. Well, I know what stopped me.

48:00.572 --> 48:04.374
And you know what?
It's never stopping me again.

